          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is your returns policy?",
            "answer": "<p>At Spicers, customer satisfaction is our priority. We offer a 14-day return policy for most products. To initiate a return, contact our Customer Service Team by phone or email for approval. Please note that a restocking fee may apply for non-defective items. Returns after 14 days or for change of mind, over-ordering, or ordering errors are not accepted. Clearance and custom products are non-returnable. We encourage you to review your order carefully before finalizing your purchase.<\/p>"
          }
        },
